Package: depcarbpexa
Title: ModelsCloud Wrapper for the Depression Carbon Footprint Markov Model
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R:
    person("Mehrshad", "Mokhtaran", email = "mehrshad.mokhtaran@ubc.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A ModelsCloud-compatible wrapper embedding a heemod-based Markov
    model that compares three depression treatment strategies (cognitive
    behavioural therapy, pharmacotherapy, combined) on healthcare costs,
    quality-adjusted life years (QALYs), and carbon footprint of care. Supports
    both single-scenario (named list) and batch (data frame) inputs, and
    optionally incorporates the social cost of carbon into incremental
    cost-effectiveness ratios.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
